<P>AS PERFORMED AT THE THEATRE-ROYAL, COVENT-GARDEN, <HI>LONDON.</HI></P>
<P><HI>BY THOMAS MORTON,</HI> OF THE HONOURABLE SOCIETY OF LINCOLN'S-INN.</P>
<P>BOSTON:</P>
<P>PRINTED AND SOLD BY WILLIAM SPOTSWOOD, SOLD ALSO BY H. <HI>&amp;</HI> P. RICE, PHILADELPHIA.</P>
<P>1794.</P>
</DIV1>
